314514663.Title: 30 in. 5.6 cu. ft. Slide-In Gas Range with Self-Cleaning Convection Oven and Air Fry in Stainless Steel, Silver
314514663.Description: At GE Appliances, we bring good things to life, by designing and building the world's best appliances. Our goal is to help people improve their lives at home by providing quality appliances that were made for real life. Whether it's enjoying the tradition of making meals from scratch or tackling a mountain of muddy jeans and soccer jerseys, GE Appliances are crafted to support any and every task in the home. 300119811.Title: Whirlpool 5.0 cu. ft. Slide-In Gas Range in White
300119811.Description: Cook for the family, even on a hectic schedule with our 5.0 cu. ft. front control gas range with cast-iron grates. This cooking range is designed with features that help you get dinner to the table quickly. Skip preheating for favorites like pizza and lasagna with FROZEN BAKE technology. Cleaning your kitchen range is simple with adjustable self-cleaning settings that take on all kinds of messes. Color: White.

302777805.Title: Whirlpool 5.8 cu. ft. Smart Slide-In Gas Range with EZ-2-LIFT Hinged Cast-Iron Grates in White
302777805.Description: Cut out routine steps and get the right settings every time with this slide-in electric range. Send YUMMLY Guided Cooking instructions directly to the smart range or use Scan-to-Cook technology to start cooking frozen foods in the self-cleaning oven using your smartphone or tablet. The stove's touchscreen provides instant accessto settings your family uses most, too. Color: White.
